00:01:02.690 --> 00:01:06.420
first Tom (diameter 10" and 8" deep),

00:01:06.620 --> 00:01:10.700
second Tom (diameter 12" and 9" deep),

00:01:10.900 --> 00:01:14.840
floor Tom (diameter16" and 16" deep)

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:19.840
 and bass drum
(diameter 22" and 18" deep).

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:22.880
The kit includes the 900-series stands:

00:01:23.250 --> 00:01:25.180
a stand for the snare drum,

